      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what do you mean a \"goblin in the warehouse\"? I don't follow that. I'm just looking for actual logistical explanations for why these specific SKUs are off by such small amounts. Can you stick to the data and give me a list of standard professional causes for this kind of shrinkage?",
